{"tid":171312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朗豪坊對面大廈墮樓 男子送院不治","createTime":"2017-03-25T08:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T14:24:14.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"273a52d26a18d52006bcae31845c00246095e951","tid":171312,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"旺角奶路臣街11號遠東發展旺角大廈，下午2時許，一名年約30歲男子，被人發現由大廈高處墮下，倒卧在7樓簷篷，重傷奄奄一息，消防員接報到場將他救下再送院，經搶救後證實不治，警員正在場調查。<br />\n<br />\n由於大廈位於朗豪坊砵蘭街方向對面，大批市民目睹墮樓事件發生。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"98915f346c0d0a5020e0e33a461643f9d120575f","tid":171312,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170325/56477741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170325%2F56477741&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=09ac903b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170325%2F56477741&h=13e5cdf2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170325/56477741</a>"},{"pid":"a2f2888983efe588bd47fd2bbecf7f88f5c71e7d","tid":171312,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:38:46.000Z","msg":"就到我"},{"pid":"e925dab0e604f009f542dccbde8d28d9af1a40bf","tid":171312,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:50:44.000Z","msg":"自殺成功"},{"pid":"7c988803812cb647949899897a916fadc011523d","tid":171312,"uid":5581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就到我</blockquote><br />\n咪咁啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750613285ac24